ca.ualberta.cmput301w14t08.geochan.models
Class FavouritesLog

java.lang.Object
  ca.ualberta.cmput301w14t08.geochan.models.FavouritesLog

public class FavouritesLog
extends java.lang.Object

Handles the threads/comments saved by the user as favourite, to be available for later viewing. Contains methods to add, remove and check presence of favourite comments/threads. Is a singleton.

Author:
Artem Chikin
